headline: Oklahoma Department of Labor Selects Tyler Technologies to Modernize Regulatory Systems
summary: PLANO, Texas, August 19, 2025--Tyler Technologies announced today that the Oklahoma Department of Labor (ODOL) has selected Tyler’s State Regulatory Platform Suite cloud solution.
